      <h1 class='title'>Organic Farming</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 27 October 2003 vol 412 c31WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_31ws' title='Col. 31WS &mdash; HC Deb 27 October 2003 vol 412 c31WS' name='column_31ws' href='#column_31ws' rel='bookmark'>31WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0412P0-04629'>
        <a name='S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_145'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-julia-drown' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_145' title='Link to this speech by Ms Julia Drown' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-julia-drown" title="Ms Julia Drown">Ms Drown</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0412P0-04629">To ask the Secretary of State for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs how much the Government spent in 2002&#x2013;03 on<span class="italic">(a)</span> research into and <span class="italic">(b)</span> support for (i) organic farming and (ii) GM crops. [132450]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0412P0-04630'>
        <a name='S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_146'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-elliot-morley' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_146' title='Link to this speech by Mr Elliot Morley' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-elliot-morley" title="Mr Elliot Morley">Mr. Morley</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0412P0-04630">The table as follows shows Defra spending in the financial year 2002&#x2013;03 on support of and research into organic farming and GM crops respectively.</p><p id="S6CV0412P0-04631"><table>
          <tr>
          <td></td>
          <td><span class="italic">Organic farming</span></td>
          <td><span class="italic">GM crops</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>Support</td>
          <td>&#x00A3;12,567,000 + &#x00A3;301,000 for the organic conversion information service</td>
          <td>&#x00A3;0</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>Research for development purposes</td>
          <td>&#x00A3;1,809,000</td>
          <td>&#x00A3;0</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>Research for the purpose of environmental risk assessment</td>
          <td>&#x00A3;0</td>
          <td>&#x00A3;4,522,000</td>
          </tr>
          </table></p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
